item.dc:creator: @owns_reece owns reece
item.description:
@owns_reece wrote:

[quote=“Andrew Ferguson, post:35, topic:400814”][quote author=rip4d link=topic=497870.msg3640959#msg3640959 date=1309006752]
Not having novicaine when getting 4 teeth pulled…
[/quote]
Omg that happened to you too? I got 4 out when I was 16 and the doctor said he gave me enough shots and then next one would put me under cause they had to cut open my gums some cause the root was too long to be pulled out directly. I couldn’t sleep for weeks after that.

Mine: I choked on a chip, fell forward slammed my head on the counter and tried to grab something, grabbed the cord to our new STEEL toaster oven (thing was like 40 pounds) and fell back pulling it and making it fall on my balls. Then I threw up because of the pain and had to sit there for 2 hours till someone got home.[/quote]
OUCH
